      <p class="standfirst">
        Your BAP still aggregates the multi-tenant seller BPP. What's new:
        once an order is confirmed on the Trade side, the BAP turns around
        and acts as a <em>Logistics BAP</em>, booking a carrier BPP (JNE)
        to collect from the store and deliver to Andi. The store hands the
        parcel to JNE; the parcel never rides a store van.
      </p>

